            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國再出拳打擊中國晶片能力 商務部準備撤銷三大廠在華豁免",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 川普政府將著手撤銷英特爾、 三星電子和SK海力士在華事業使用美國技術的豁免，再次意圖打擊中國獲取先進晶片製造技術的能力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據刊登在美國聯邦公報上的文件，上述公司在豁免到期前還有120天的時間。相關企業可以申請許可證以繼續運營。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三星和SK海力士的相當一部分內存晶片產能都依賴中國。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Removes China Waivers for Intel, Samsung and SK Hynix</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%86%8D%E5%87%BA%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B-%E5%95%86%E5%8B%99%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E6%92%A4%E9%8A%B7%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%A0%E5%9C%A8%E8%8F%AF%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D-135012027.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 22:25:47",
