        {
            "title": "加拿大經濟出現接近兩年來首次萎縮 貿易戰重創出口",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 由於與美國的貿易戰擠壓了出口和企業投資，第二季度<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:加拿大;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/加拿大\">加拿大</a>經濟出現接近兩年來首次萎縮。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加拿大統計局周五在渥太華公佈的數據顯示，第二季度國內生產毛額折合年率萎縮1.6%。這是自新冠疫情以來的最大降幅，也是近兩年來的首次萎縮。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然大體符合加拿大央行的預測，但這一結果比彭博對經濟學家的調查預期更糟，後者預計為下降0.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於美國對加拿大商品加徵關稅嚴重打擊了出口，第二季度出口折合年率下降27%，超過了第一季度出口商搶跑川普關稅而帶來的短暫提振。進口下降了5.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">企業投資在第一季度僅成長1.1%後，第二季度收縮10.1%，凸顯出在面對美國關稅和政策的不斷變化及不確定性之際，加拿大企業的悲觀情緒加劇。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Canada’s Economy Shrinks in Second Quarter as Exports Crushed</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Mario Baker Ramirez.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E8%90%8E%E7%B8%AE-%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E9%87%8D%E5%89%B5%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3-125306292.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 21:35:38",
