        },
        {
            "title": "美債市場通膨衡量指標創六個月新高 凸顯投資者憂心聯儲會獨立性受損",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_yxxFiR_TEKGLD42xCLkdg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8b291dfd5f7f5610616e92e6c8631dcc\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 儘管川普對<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>的攻擊升級，但本周美債市場走勢相對平靜。然而，通膨預期的進一步上升表明，投資者對川普試圖左右央行決策的擔憂加劇。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周三，美國10年期盈虧平衡通膨率（即美國國債與通膨掛鉤債券的殖利率差）升至2.46%的六個月高位，周五回落至2.41%。這一走勢源於通膨保值債券(TIPS)殖利率的下行；隨著對沖需求增加，該殖利率下跌至1.81%的四個月低點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日前，川普敦促聯儲會決策者降息，令外界擔心若過早行動可能損害央行控制通膨的能力。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Z6m9ZfBqEEvjFVLP6Im2Xg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f0d455980db83783ff9e9237bde6d77e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">名義10年期國債殖利率本周收盤勢將基本持平。周五該殖利率小幅上升2個基點至4.22%，接近8月區間的下端。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美銀利率策略師Meghan Swiber表示，隨著投資者對沖聯儲會失去一定獨立性的風險，盈虧平衡通膨率有更大的表現空間，「在通膨高企和勞動力市場持堅的情況下激進降息將引發聯儲會政策失誤。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她預計10年期盈虧平衡通膨率將升至2.55%。本月，該指標已上漲3個基點，處於過去兩年2%-2.5%區間的上端。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然本周變動幅度相對較小，但該指標的穩步走升是相當明確的跡象，凸顯出投資者越來越擔心川普攻擊聯儲會會破壞其控制通膨的公信力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近幾周，長期債券表現遜於短期債券，30年期與5年期美國國債的殖利率差擴大至2001年以來最大水平。在鮑威爾上周於傑克遜霍爾研討會上為降息打開大門後，該利差進一步擴大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bond Market’s Inflation Gauge Touches Six-Month High on Fed Risk</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Alice Gledhill.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%82%B5%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E8%A1%A1%E9%87%8F%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%99%E5%89%B5%E5%85%AD%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E5%87%B8%E9%A1%AF%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E6%86%82%E5%BF%83%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%80%A7%E5%8F%97%E6%90%8D-120001509.html",
